OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FDisabled man joins Europe's
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fastronaut programme        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A disabled British man has been chosen 
OL,6, for astronaut training by Europe's     
OL,7, space agency, a world first.           
OL,9,FJohn McFall, 41, joined 16 men and     
OL,10,Fwomen selected for the European Space  
OL,11,FAgency's (Esa) first new class of      
OL,12,Fastronauts in 13 years.                
OL,14,FHis right leg was amputated after a    
OL,15,Fmotorcycle crash when he was 19. He    
OL,16,Fbecame a professional athlete and      
OL,17,Frepresented Team GB at the Paralympics.
OL,19,FAnother British woman, Rosemary Coogan,
OL,20,Fwas selected as a career astronaut.    
